In England, in the seven days to 11 November, there were 205,966 new confirmed cases (364.2 new cases per 100,000). In the seven days to 04 November, there were 211,207 new cases, and so the new cases have decreased by 2% (5,241 fewer cases). The number of confirmed COVID-19 cases in England so far as at 16 November is 8,175,202 (14,456.6 cases per 100,000 population).
